videos.description: Luka Garza pushes his way into the paint and to the hoop for a tough Iowa basket vs. Ohio State.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Garza flexes to celebrate tough jumper) 2020/2/20

videos.headline: Garza flexes to celebrate tough jumper

videos.description: Luka Garza keeps Iowa ahead in the first half with a smooth jumper while absorbing contact.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Garza sticks with it for an Iowa and-1) 2020/2/20

videos.headline: Garza sticks with it for an Iowa and-1

videos.description: Luka Garza calls for the ball down the stretch from Joe Toussaint as he beats Ohio State's Kaleb Wesson to the paint for a contested lay-in.

videos.description: Cordell Pemsl works his Ohio State defender into the paint and puts up a jumper for an Iowa bucket.

videos.description: Joe Wieskamp drives from the elbow to the hoop through multiple Ohio State defenders before rising up for a posterizing slam in the second half.
